# =============================================================================
# forge-studio-lite — Variables de entorno
# Copia este archivo a `.env`. `.env` está en .gitignore.
#
# TODAS las keys son OPCIONALES. Las variantes (a) typographic y (b) photo+gradient
# NO necesitan ninguna key. Solo la variante (c) "stock" lee estas, y solo la que
# corresponda al "source" de tu stock-queries.json.
# =============================================================================

# -- Carousel image sourcing — variante (c) -----------------------------------
# Royalty-free, publicable. Keys gratis:
#   Pexels   → https://www.pexels.com/api/        (Pexels License, uso comercial OK)
#   Unsplash → https://unsplash.com/developers     (Unsplash License)
# PEXELS_API_KEY=
# UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY=
